# Data Layer

## Schema & migrations
- DB: {{DATABASE}}.
- Migrations: {{MIGRATION_TOOL}}; every schema change goes through a migration, never edited by hand.
- Table/column naming: {{DB_NAMING}}.

## Query patterns
- Access the DB via {{DATA_ACCESS_PATTERN}} (e.g. repository); don't scatter raw queries everywhere.
- Avoid N+1; index hot queries.

## Rules
- No business logic in the DB layer.
- Use transactions for multi-step operations that must be atomic.
